          "description": "I\u2019ve had the best dental cleaning of my life. It was thorough, significantly improved the look of my teeth, and I barely felt anything.\n\nMy husband had an emergency tooth extraction, and Dr. Armstrong was wonderful with him. She also did my dental exam and never pushed any unnecessary procedures\u2014she simply gave her professional opinion and reassured me when I was worried about my husband.\n\nThe front desk staff are polite, personable, and accommodating. They work with most major insurance providers and clearly explain in advance what may not be covered, so there are no surprises.\n\nOverall, it was a wonderful experience, and I cannot recommend this clinic enough.",
