          "description": "I\u2019ve never been a fan of going to dentist visits. I came across this location thru my insurance and decided to give it a try since it\u2019s about a block away from my job. I truly found my dentist home. It\u2019s been about a year since I started here and have had multiple visits with Violet, she makes my dentists visits so exciting. My teeth and gums have improved , her words of affirmation and work on my teeth have motivated me to do better.",
