          "description": "Today I met with Dr. Clay and dental hygienist, Violet. From the moment I was welcomed in by the receptionist, I was made to feel comfortable. Violet did a wonderful job taking me through the x-rays, scanning, and dental cleaning. She thoroughly explained each step and answered my questions. Dr. Clay followed up with his exam and review of my x-rays and scans. It was a very thorough appointment.",
