          "description": "The staff:\nSuper friendly, knowledgeable, professional, amazing.\n\nThe space:\nClean, state of the art, warm.\n\nThis has been my dentist for many, many, many years. I had an appointment with a new hygienists today and was reminded why I love everyone here.  Professionalism. Prowess. Friendliness.\n\nI used to hate dentists and going to the dentist. I went because I had to. I had sensitivity to cold, cavities, too much build up. Everything changed when I started going to MDG. With their help and recommendations my teeth have never been healthier. it\u2019s thanks to the amazing doctors and hygienists  here.\n\nNow I just drop by to say hello when I\u2019m near by because they bring me joy. I am so happy that I found MDG.",
